bbf2-6d87-4287-900e-441760d3a8f9%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Our%20review%20of%20the%20Narwal%20S20%20vacuum%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EOur%20review%20of%20the%20Narwal%20S20%20vacuum%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Narwal%20S20%20Pro%20smart%20mod%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F675321de8fbb2783ed3041d9%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222268%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Narwal%20S20%20Pro%20has%20five%20modes%20including%20Smart%2C%20Suction%2C%20Turbo%2C%20Quiet%2C%20and%20Max%20for%20cleaning%20floors.%3Cp%3EAlex%20Temblador%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI've%20been%20using%20the%20Narwal%20S20%20Pro%20to%20keep%201%2C600%20square%20feet%20of%20historic%20hardwood%20and%20laminate%20floors%20clean.%20In%20addition%20to%20running%20some%20specific%20tests%20on%20both%20floor%20types%2C%20I've%20been%20using%20it%20once%20a%20week%20to%20clean%20my%20floors.%20Keep%20reading%20to%20see%20how%20the%20Narwal%20S20%20Pro%20works.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22afd31fcb-ab3b-4b42-9a8d-ec28063cd19d%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Overall%20Ease%20of%20Use%5C%22%3EOverall%20Ease%20of%20Use%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Narwal%20S20%20Pro%20screen%20reads%20dirt%20detected%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F675321dd4adc4cc1343507c4%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222268%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20small%20LCD%20screen%20alerts%20you%20to%20whether%20dirt%20has%20been%20detected%20and%20adjusts%20suction%20and%20water%20output%20accordingly.%3Cp%3EAlex%20Temblador%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAt%209.41%20pounds%2C%20the%20Narwal%20S20%20Pro%20is%20lightweight%2C%20and%20also%20has%20a%20self-propel%20system%20and%20a%20vacuum%20head%20that%20easily%20swivels%20about.%20The%20handle%20is%20comfortable%20and%20outfitted%20with%20a%20small%20LED%20screen%2C%20a%20power%20button%2C%20and%20a%20button%20to%20switch%20modes.%20There%20are%20five%20modes%3A%20Smart%2C%20Suction%2C%20Turbo%2C%20Quiet%2C%20and%20Max.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESmart%20mode%20detects%20when%20floors%20are%20dirty%20and%20adjusts%20the%20suction%20and%20mopping%20capabilities%2C%20while%20Quiet%20mode%20results%20in%20a%20low%20noise-cleaning%20experience%20and%20a%20longer%20battery%20life.%20Suction%20mode%20can%20be%20used%20to%20remove%20a%20build-up%20of%20water%20on%20the%20floor%2C%20while%20Turbo%20and%20Max%20modes%20are%20to%20be%20employed%20on%20stubborn%20stains.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20Smart%20mode%2C%20the%20LCD%20screen%20turns%20yellow%20when%20dirt%20is%20detected%20and%20then%20blue%20when%20the%20floor%20is%20clean.%20The%20only%20mode%20that%20you%20can't%20switch%20to%20with%20the%20mode%20button%20is%20Max%20mode.%20There%20is%20a%20small%20trigger%20underneath%20the%20handle%2C%20and%20it%20is%20through%20continuously%20holding%20the%20trigger%20that%20the%20Max%20mode%20can%20be%20used.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Narwal%20S20%20Pro's%20handle%20can%20be%20leaned%20180%20degrees%20or%20all%20the%20way%20to%20the%20ground.%20With%20a%20180-degree%20handle%2C%20I%20can%20reach%20further%20under%20furniture.%20In%20this%20position%2C%20the%20vacuum%20increases%20the%20suction%20and%20mopping%20capabilities%20automatically%20as%20it%20senses%20that%20you're%20cleaning%20in%20a%20typically%20dustier%20place%20(like%20under%20your%20bed).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EVoice%20prompts%20also%20sound%20when%20issues%20occur%2C%20such%20as%20the%20roller%20brush%20not%20being%20in%20place%20or%20the%20dirty%20water%20tank%20being%20full.%20When%20placed%20in%20the%20upright%20position%2C%20the%20wet-dry%20vacuum%20will%20pause.%20The%20Narwal%20S20%20Pro%20is%20not%20outfitted%20with%20LED%20lights%2C%20which%20is%20a%20drawback.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%229dc4627e-f448-4802-ba6d-34d789961591%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Cleaning%20Performance%5C%22%3ECleaning%20Performance%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Narwal%20S20%20Pro%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F675321dd4adc4cc1343507c5%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222268%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EIn%20addition%20to%20wiping%20up%20stuck%20on%20dirt%20and%20loose%20debris%20with%20ease%2C%20the%20Narwal%20S20%20also%20did%20a%20great%20job%20getting%20close%20up%20with%20edges%20and%20can%20lay%20flat%20to%20get%20into%20low-lying%20areas.%3Cp%3EAlex%20Temblador%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EOverall%2C%20the%20Narwal%20S20%20Pro%20does%20a%20good%20job%20cleaning%20dust%2C%20dirt%2C%20debris%2C%20and%20hair%20from%20hard%20floors.%20I%20was%20very%20impressed%20by%20the%20edge%20cleaning.%20Although%20most%20wet-dry%20vacuums%20say%20they%20have%20close-edge%20cleaning%2C%20the%20Narwal%20S20%20Pro%20actually%20does.%20When%20I%20cleaned%20a%20wall%20with%20the%20edge%20of%20the%20vacuum%2C%20there%20was%20no%20dry%20space%20between%20the%20vacuum%20and%20the%20wall.%20I've%20never%20seen%20that%20before.%20Also%2C%20it%20cleans%20up%20to%20a%20quarter-inch%20from%20the%20front%20edge%20of%20the%20vacuum%20head.%20Most%20wet-dry%20vacuums%20I've%20tested%20have%20a%20half-inch%20front%20edge%20cleaning.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20covered%20my%20floors%20with%20a%20variety%20of%20materials%20%E2%80%94%20coffee%2C%20flour%2C%20cereal%2C%20barbecue%20sauce%2C%20dried%20ketchup%2C%20soda%2C%20and%20syrup%20%E2%80%94%20to%20see%20how%20well%20the%20wet-dry%20vacuum%20cleans.%20The%20Narwal%20S20%20Pro%20cleaned%20up%20all%20the%20materials%20in%20a%20single%20pass%2C%20at%20least%20when%20vacuuming%20in%20a%20forward%20motion.%20Unfortunately%2C%20when%20vacuuming%20in%20reverse%2C%20the%20Narwal%20S20%20Pro%20doesn't%20do%20a%20good%20job.%20Coffee%20and%20cereal%20would%20get%20caught%20behind%20the%20wheels.%20It%20did%20a%20little%20better%20with%20cleaning%20substances%20in%20reverse%2C%20but%20still%2C%20I%20had%20to%20clean%20the%20substances%20in%20a%20forward%20motion%20to%20ensure%20I%20cleaned%20the%20floor%20thoroughly.%20Poor%20reverse%20cleaning%20is%20the%20biggest%20drawback%20of%20this%20vacuum.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20on%20Smart%20mode%2C%20the%20dirty%20water%20tank%20needed%20to%20be%20emptied%20at%2021%20minutes%2C%20which%20was%20the%20exact%20moment%20I%20finished%20cleaning%20my%20house.%20The%20clean%20water%20tank%20lasted%20until%2034%20minutes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22882ffc96-46bb-4c6d-bfb9-2cf8b7e44042%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Battery%20Life%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EBattery%20Life%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20brand%2C%20the%20Narwal%20S20%20Pro's%20battery%20can%20last%20up%20to%2060%20minutes.%20However%2C%20this%20is%20only%20the%20case%20if%20you%20use%20the%20wet-dry%20vacuum%20in%20Quiet%20mode.%20When%20I%20tested%20the%20Narwal%20S20%20Pro%20in%20Quiet%20mode%2C%20it%20lasted%2058%20minutes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20testing%20the%20wet-dry%20vacuum%20on%20the%20Smart%20Mode%2C%20which%20adjusts%20the%20suction%20and%20mopping%20capabilities%20depending%20on%20how%20dirty%20the%20surface%20is%2C%20the%20Narwal%20S20%20Pro%20battery%20lasted%2039%20minutes.%20A%20low%20battery%20indicator%20came%20on%20at%2037%20minutes.%20I%20was%20pleasantly%20surprised%20that%20in%20Turbo%20mode%2C%20the%20Narwal%20S20%20Pro%20lasted%2036%20minutes.%20Typically%2C%20you%20don't%20see%20high-powered%20cleaning%20modes%20lasting%20more%20than%2020%20minutes%2C%20so%20this%20is%20a%20win%20in%20my%20book.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20battery%20takes%20about%20three%20hours%20to%20fully%20recharge%2C%20which%20is%20standard%20for%20most%20wet-dry%20vacuums.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2235573c32-93f5-4850-832e-fd983d8b5969%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Maintenance%20and%20Cleaning%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EMaintenance%20and%20Cleaning%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Narwal%20S20%20Pro%20body%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F675321de4adc4cc1343507c6%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222268%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20separate%20clean%20and%20dirty%20water%20tanks%20are%20located%20on%20the%20rear%20of%20the%20device.%20Narwal%20also%20separates%20the%20collected%20solid%20debris%20from%20the%20dirty%20water%20with%20a%20built-in%20cage%20design.%3Cp%3EAlex%20Temblador%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Narwal%20S20%20Pro%20is%20equipped%20with%20an%20impressive%20self-cleaning%20and%20self-drying%20system%2C%20which%20makes%20it%20one%20of%20the%20easiest%20wet-dry%20vacuums%20on%20the%20market%20to%20clean%20and%20maintain.%20After%20placing%20the%20vacuum%20on%20the%20base%2C%20I%20emptied%20the%20dirty%20water%20tank.%20Narwal%20has%20designed%20the%20tank%20so%20that%20debris%20is%20separated%20from%20the%20dirty%20water%20by%20a%20built-in%20cage.%20The%20debris%20will%20be%20wet%2C%20so%20you'll%20have%20to%20use%20the%20cleaning%20brush%20provided%20to%20dump%20it%20into%20the%20trash%20can.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFrom%20there%2C%20I%20pushed%20the%20self-cleaning%20button.%20Users%20can%20choose%20between%20having%20the%20self-cleaning%20and%20self-drying%20systems%20run%20one%20after%20another%20or%20as%20separate%20functions.%20For%20instance%2C%20if%20you%20want%20to%20do%20a%20second%20round%20of%20self-drying%2C%20you%20can%20do%20that%20and%20forgo%20the%20self-cleaning%20system%20in%20that%20instance.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESelf-cleaning%20lasts%203-5%20minutes%2C%20while%20self-drying%20takes%20at%20least%2030%20minutes.%20The%20self-cleaning%20time%20is%20determined%20by%20the%20dirt%20level.%20When%20the%20self-cleaning%20system%20is%20employed%2C%20it%20disinfects%20the%20roller%20brush%20with%20high-temperature%20water.%20The%20Narwal%20S20%20Pro%20adjusts%20the%20drying%20time%20depending%20on%20the%20brush%20roll's%20humidity.%20It%20also%20air%20dries%20the%20pipe%20and%20filter%20with%20hot%20air.%20Once%20the%20self-cleaning%20and%20self-drying%20system%20was%20complete%2C%20I%20removed%20the%20dirty%20water%20tank%20and%20emptied%20it.%20Debris%20is%20separated%20from%20the%20dirty%20water%20making%20it%20easier%20to%20dispose%20of%20the%20debris%20with%20the%20cleaning%20brush%20provided.%20(The%20debris%20was%20wet%2C%20so%20it%20does%20take%20some%20effort%20to%20remove%20it%20from%20the%20tank.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20removed%20the%20vacuum%20head%20and%20brush%20roll%20when%20the%20self-cleaning%20and%20self-drying%20systems%20were%20finished.%20I%20couldn't%20believe%20the%20brush%20roll%20was%20actually%20dry%2C%20which%20is%20not%20the%20case%20for%20most%20wet-dry%20vacuum%20self-drying%20systems.%20There%20was%20also%20no%20dust%20or%20debris%20under%20the%20vacuum%20head%2C%20which%20is%20something%20I%20usually%20discover%20with%20other%20wet-dry%20vacuums.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20only%20other%20maintenance%20required%20of%20users%20is%20to%20replace%20the%20filter%20when%20necessary.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2260435661-709d-4ecc-8f67-f73985e0f278%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Filtration%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EFiltration%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20wet-dry%20vacuum%20is%20outfitted%20with%20a%20filter%20located%20at%20the%20top%20of%20the%20dirty%20water%20tank.%20When%20cleaning%20the%20wet-dry%20vacuum%2C%20the%20filter%20needs%20to%20be%20removed%20and%20cleaned%20with%20water.%20It%20should%20be%20completely%20dry%20before%20being%20placed%20back%20on%20the%20dirty%20water%20tank.%20An%20additional%20filter%20is%20provided%20so%20that%20whenever%20you%20need%20to%20exchange%20it%2C%20you%20have%20one%20on%20hand.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22e7ab6578-792d-4b6e-9ede-6057798a3552%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Cons%20to%20consider%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ECons%20to%20consider%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20two%20notable%20cons%20of%20the%20Narwal%20S20%20Pro.%20For%20one%2C%20it%20lacks%20LED%20lighting.%20I'm%20not%20sure%20why%20Narwal%20forwent%20this%20feature%2C%20but%20it%20would%20be%20helpful%20in%20cleaning%20in%20low%20lit%20areas.%20The%20other%20con%3F%20The%20Narwal%20S20%20Pro%20does%20not%20vacuum%20or%20mop%20well%20in%20reverse.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlthough%20the%20Narwal%20S20%20Pro%20picked%20up%20all%20the%20different%20materials%20and%20substances%20on%20the%20ground%20in%20one%20pass%20during%20the%20testing%20period%2C%20I%20have%20to%20note%20that%20when%20I%20say%20%26quot%3Bone%20pass%2C%26quot%3B%20I%20mean%20when%20vacuuming%20in%20a%20forward%20direction.%20When%20I%20pulled%20the%20Narwal%20S20%20Pro%20backward%20or%20vacuumed%20in%20reverse%20over%20different%20materials%2C%20it%20did%20a%20very%20poor%20job%20of%20suctioning%20and%20mopping.%20Coffee%2C%20cereal%2C%20and%20flour%20got%20stuck%20behind%20the%20wheels.%20I%20also%20noticed%20other%20debris%2C%20like%20leaves%20and%20dried%20mud%2C%20not%20getting%20picked%20up%20by%20the%20Narwal%20S20%20Pro%20when%20vacuuming%20in%20reverse%2C%20which%20resulted%20in%20more%20effort%20and%20cleaning%20time%20on%20my%20behalf.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22ac48941f-96f1-4601-8cf4-a886c0c0b26b%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22What%20are%20your%20alternatives%3F%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20are%20your%20alternatives%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Tineco%20Floor%20One%20S7%20Pro%20%20being%20used%20on%20a%20hardwood%20floor%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65afdc396c8f0a134f792693%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222268%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Tineco%20Pure%20One%20S7%20Pro%20cleaned%20wet%20and%20dry%20debris%20with%20ease%20and%20has%20an%20LCD%20interface%20that%20indicates%20a%20dirt%20detection%20alert%2C%20modes%2C%20battery%20life%2C%20and%20more.%20It's%20self-cleaning%20system%20is%20slightly%20more%20involved%20but%20it%20does%20have%20LED%20lights%20to%20guide%20the%20way.%3Cp%3EAlex%20Temblador%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhome%2Ftineco-floor-one-s7-pro-review%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20Tineco%20Floor%20One%20S7%20Pro%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%3FamazonTrackingID%3Dbiauto-56307-20%26h%3Db4510bec69f683fbe7d1349383236dfc7c284359ee0e3eb4c0306c133b86ad9b%26postID%3D67531fe6db9a57fe962ac924%26postSlug%3Dguides%252Fhome%252Fnarwal-s20-pro-vacuum-mop-review%26site%3Dbi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.amazon.com%252FTineco-ONE-S5-Lightweight-Multi-Surface%252Fdp%252FB09P2RKRWX%253Fth%253D1%5C%22%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETineco%20Floor%20One%20S5%20%3C%2Fa%3Eare%20probably%20the%20biggest%20competitors%20to%20the%20Narwal%20S20%20Pro.%20The%20Tineco%20wet-dry%20vacuums%20might%20have%20slightly%20less%20impressive%20edge%20cleaning%2C%20but%20they%20have%20a%20similar%20number%20of%20cleaning%20modes%20(including%20a%20dirt%20detect%20mode)%2C%20LCD%20screens%2C%20and%20voice%20commands.%20They%20excel%20far%20better%20in%20reverse%20cleaning%20than%20the%20Narwal%20S20%20Pro.%20I%20wish%20the%20Tineco%20Floor%20One%20S7%20Pro's%20self-cleaning%20and%20self-drying%20system%20was%20more%20like%20the%20Narwal%20S20%20Pro%2C%20however%2C%20I%20will%20say%20that%20I%20prefer%20the%20dirt%20detect%20indicator%20on%20the%20Tineco%20Floor%20One%20S7%20Pro%20and%20Tineco%20Floor%20One%20S5%20than%20the%20Narwal%20S20%20Pro's.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhere%20the%20Narwal%20S20%20Pro%20can%20clean%20hard%20floors%20only%2C%20the%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhome%2Fbest-wet-dry-vacuums%23most-versatile%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3