at%20a%20hospital%2C%20were%20the%20two%20cases.%20A%20two-month-old%20was%20also%20found%20infected%20in%20Ahmedabad.%20One%20case%20was%20each%20reported%20in%20Chennai%20and%20Salem.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20affected%20infants%20and%20their%20families%20in%20Bengaluru%20and%20Ahmedabad%20have%20no%20recent%20travel%20history%2C%20the%20Union%20health%20ministry%20has%20said%2C%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fhmpv-already-in-circulation-including-in-india-top-medical-body-icmr-7410226%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eruling%20out%20exposure%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20other%20regions%20or%20countries.%20There%20was%20no%20immediate%20statement%20on%20the%20cases%20in%20Tamil%20Nadu.%20The%20HMPV%20is%20a%20globally%20recognised%20respiratory%20virus%20that%20recently%20gained%20attention%20after%20its%20outbreak%20was%20reported%20in%20China.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ministry%20said%20it%20is%20monitoring%20the%20situation%20through%20all%20available%20surveillance%20channels.%20The%20Indian%20Council%20of%20Medical%20Research%20(IMCR)%20will%20continue%20to%20track%20trends%20in%20HMPV%20circulation%20throughout%20the%20year%2C%20it%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20governments%20in%20Karnataka%2C%20Maharashtra%20and%20Delhi%20have%20issued%20guidelines%20-%20similar%20to%20those%20followed%20during%20Covid-19%20-%20to%20ensure%20preparedness%20for%20potential%20health%20challenges%20related%20to%20HMPV.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHMPV%2C%20first%20identified%20in%202001%2C%20is%20a%20respiratory%20infection%20that%20causes%20flu-like%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fhealth%2Fhealth-ministry-confirms-two-hmpv-cases-in-india-know-symptoms-and-prevention-steps-7410083%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esymptoms%3C%2Fa%3E.%20It%20can%20affect%20people%20of%20all%20ages%2C%20although%20children%20below%20five%20years%20of%20age%2C%20older%20adults%20and%20those%20with%20weakened%20immune%20systems%20are%20at%20a%20