nce%20in%20the%20ongoing%20rescue%20operation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EWe%20have%20requested%20the%20Army's%20assistance%20in%20the%20ongoing%20rescue%20operation.%20The%20State%20Disaster%20Response%20Force%20(SDRF)%20and%20the%20National%20Disaster%20Response%20Force%20(NDRF)%20are%20also%20on%20their%20way%20to%20the%20incident%20site%20to%20aid%20in%20the%20efforts.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2F35ET3f80jr%5C%22%3Ehttps%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2F35ET3f80jr%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Himanta%20Biswa%20Sarma%20(%40himantabiswa)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhimantabiswa%2Fstatus%2F1876263037298155877%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EJanuary%206%2C%202025%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BRat%20hole%26quot%3B%20mining%20is%20a%20hazardous%20technique%20where%20narrow%20tunnels%20are%20manually%20dug%20by%20workers.%20These%20tunnels%20lead%20to%20deep%20pits%20from%20which%20coal%20is%20mined.%20They%20also%20harm%20the%20environment%20because%20the%20acidic%20water%20and%20heavy%20metals%20discharged%20from%20the%20mines%20are%20toxic%20to%20water%20sources%20used%20for%20agriculture%20and%20human%20consumption.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202018%2C%2015%20miners%20were%20trapped%20in%20an%20illegal%20coal%20mine%20in%20the%20East%20Jaintia%20Hills%20district%20in%20Meghalaya%20after%20water%20from%20a%20nearby%20river%20gushed%20into%20it.%20Only%20two%20bodies%20were%20the%20National%20Disaster%20Response%20Force%20had%20seen%2C%20the%20then%20commandant%2C%20SK%20Sastri%2C%20had%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202019%2C%20Meghalaya%20was%20fined%20Rs%20100%20crore%20by%20the%20National%20Green%20Tribunal%20(NGT)%20for%20failing%20to%20curb%20illegal%20coal%20mining%20in%20the%20state.%20The%20NGT%20had%20found%20that%20most%20of%20the%2024%2C000%20mines%20in%20the%20state%20were%20illegal.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1