3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fshreyas-talpade-says-people-miss-comedy-films-what-has-happened-today-is-ott%2Farticleshow%2F116998710.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Prashant%20Kishor%20On%20Why%20He%20Rejected%20Bail%20And%20Decided%20To%20Go%20To%20Jail%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EPrashant%20Kishor%2C%20who%20was%20detained%20during%20a%20fast-unto-death%20protest%20at%20Patna's%20Gandhi%20Maidan%2C%20was%20sent%20to%20jail%20today%20even%20after%20he%20was%20granted%20bail%20by%20a%20court%20in%20Patna.%20Speaking%20to%20reporters%20outside%20the%20court%2C%20Mr%20Kishor%2C%20founder%20of%20Jan%20Suraaj%20and%20political%20strategist-turned-activist%2C%20explained%20why%20he%20refused%20to%20sign%20a%20bail%20bond.%20%26quot%3BI%20was%20taken%20to%20the%20court%20and%20I%20was%20granted%20bail%20but%20in%20the%20bail%20order%20it%20was%20mentioned%20that%20I%20should%20not%20do%20any%20wrongdoings%2C%20so%20I%20rejected%20it%20and%20I%20accepted%20to%20go%20to%20jail%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Kishor%2C%20however%2C%20was%20later%20released%20from%20police%20custody%20after%20a%20Patna%20civil%20court%20granted%20him%20bail.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20former%20poll%20strategist%20has%20been%20on%20the%20hunger%20strike%20for%20the%20last%20five%20days.%20He%20is%20demanding%20the%20cancellation%20of%20a%20Bihar%20Public%20Service%20Commission%20(BPSC)%20exam%20following%20allegations%20of%20a%20question%20paper%20leak.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPrashant%20Kishor%20also%20narrated%20the%20sequence%20of%20events%20this%20morning%3A%20%26quot%3BAround%204%20am%20today%2C%20police%20reached%20Gandhi%20Maidan%2C%20where%20I%20have%20been%20sitting%20on%20an%20indefinite%20fast%20unto%20death%20for%20the%20last%20five%20days.%20They%20told%20me%20that%20they%20were%20detaining%20me%20and%20asked%20me%20to%20go%20with%20them.%20I%20left%20with%20them.%20Since%20my%20supporters%20were%20also%20with%20me%2C%20it's%20natural%20that%20a%20minor%20clash%20broke%20out%20(between%20them%20and%20the%20police).%20But%20by%20and%20large%2C%20the%20behaviour%20of%20the%20police%20was%20not%20wrong.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20police%2C%20the%20protest%20was%20deemed%20illegal%20as%20it%20took%20place%20in%20a%20restricted%20area.%20The%20Patna%20District%20Magistrate%20has%20said%20that%20repeated%20notices%20were%20issued%2C%20urging%20Mr%20Kishor%20and%20his%20supporters%20to%20relocate%20the%20demonstration%20to%20Gardani%20Bagh%2C%20the%20designated%20protest%20site.%20Mr%20Kishor%20and%2043%20supporters%20were%20detained%2C%20and%20vehicles%2C%20including%20tractors%2C%20were%20seized%20during%20the%20operation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20some%20reports%2C%20Prashant%20Kishor%20was%20slapped%20and%20mistreated%20during%20the%20detention.%20The%20police%20denied%20all%20the%20allegations.%C2%A0Mr%20Kishor%20has%20also%20denied%20these%20reports%2C%20saying%2C%20%26quot%3BThere%20were%20some%20reports%20that%20a%20policeman%20slapped%20me.%20No%20one%20slapped%20me.%20One%20of%20my%20aides%20was%20holding%20my%20hand%20as%20he%20didn't%20want%20me%20to%20leave.%20A%20police%20official%20tried%20to%20remove%20his%20hand%20from%20my%20arm%20so%20that%20I%20could%20leave.%20I%20don't%20have%20any%20complaints%20about%20the%20behaviour%20of%20the%20police%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20was%20taken%20to%20Patna%20AIIMS%20for%20a%20medical%20check-up%20but%20the%20administration%20refused%20to%20admit%20him%2C%20Mr%20Kishor%20claimed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAfter%20we%20left%20Gandhi%20Maidan%2C%20the%20police%20didn't%20tell%20me%20where%20they%20were%20taking%20me.%20They%20took%20me%20to%20AIIMS.%20I%20was%20there%20for%20more%20than%20an%20hour.%20They%20refused%20to%20admit%20me%20and%20I%20have%20no%20idea%20why.%20The%20police%20then%20tried%20to%20take%20me%20to%20a%20different%20hospital%20but%20by%20then%20a%20large%20crowd%20of%20my%20supporters%20had%20gathered%20at%20the%20gate%20of%20AIIMS.%20There%20was%20again%20a%20minor%20clash%20at%20the%20gate.%20From%20there%2C%20the%20behaviour%20of%20the%20police%20started%20deteriorating%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFrom%205%20am%20to%2011%20am%2C%20I%20was%20made%20to%20sit%20in%20the%20police%20vehicle%20and%20they%20kept%20taking%20me%20to%20different%20places.%20They%20told%20me%20they%20would%20either%20take%20me%20to%20PMCH%20or%20NMCH%20but%20eventually%2C%20after%20five%20hours%2C%20they%20took%20me%20to%20Fatuha's%20community%20centre.%20They%20want%20to%20conduct%20my%20medical%20test%20and%20get%20a%20certificate%20from%20the%20doctors%20there.%20I%20refused%20to%20give%20my%20consent%20for%20that%20because%20I%20wasn't%20involved%20in%20any%20criminal%20activity.%20Police%20tried%20to%20convince%20the%20doctors%20for%20a%20certificate%20but%20they%20refused%20to%20give%20any%20such%20illegal%20certificate%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Kishor%20alleged.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20claimed%20that%20the%20police's%20argument%20was%20that%20they%20had%20to%20take%20a%20%26quot%3Blonger%20route%20for%20crowd%20management%26quot%3B.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BPSC%20conducted%20a%20retest%20on%20January%204%20for%20select%20candidates%20affected%20by%20the%20controversy.%20Out%20of%2012%2C012%20eligible%20candidates%2C%20only%205%2C943%20appeared%20for%20the%20examination.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20issue%20has%20also%20reached%20the%20Supreme%20Court%2C%20where%20petitioners%20are%20seeking%20the%20cancellation%20of%20the%20December%2013%20exam%20and%20action%20against%20officials%20allegedly%20using%20excessive%20force%20on%20protestors.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1736173260000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-01%2Fhf2dl0mo_prashant-kishore_625x300_06_January_25.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fprashant-kishor-sent-to-jail-after-he-refuses-to-sign-bail-bond-7411245%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Prashant%20Kishor%2C%20founder%20of%20Jan%20Suraaj%20and%20political%20strategist-turned-activist%2C%20was%20arrested%20today%20during%20his%20fast-unto-death%20protest%20at%20Patna's%20Gandhi%20Maidan.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fprashant-kishor-sent-to-jail-after-he-refuses-to-sign-bail-bond-7411245%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BWhy%20Don't%20You%20Want%20Probe%3F%26quot%3B%20High%20Court%20To%20Techie%20Atul%20Subhash's%20Wife%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EKarnataka%20High%20Court%20on%20Monday%20rejected%20the%20plea%20for%20cancelling%20the%20First%20Information%20Report%20(FIR)%C2%A0%20against%20Nikita%20Singhania%20in%20connection%20with%20the%20alleged%20suicide%20case%20of%20Bengaluru%20techie%20Atul%20Subhash.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESubhash%2C%20an%20automobile%20company%20employee%20in%20Bengaluru%2C%20had%20died%20by%20suicide%20over%20alleged%20torture%20and%20demand%20of%20Rs%203%20crore%20by%20his%20wife%20Nikita%20Singhania%20for%20divorce%20settlement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20single%20bench%20headed%20by%20Justice%20SR%20Krishna%20Kumar%20passed%20the%20order%20orally.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bench%20in%20disapproval%20of%20the%20demand%20by%20Subhash's%20wife%20stated%20that%20the%20FIR%20gives%20out%20everything%20to%20file%20the%20case%20under%20abetment%20of%20suicide.%20%26quot%3BWhat%20more%20the%20bench%20can%20look%20into%3F%26quot%3B%20the%20bench%20said.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20prima%20facie%20ingredients%20of%20the%20offence%20are%20made%20out%20in%20the%20complaint.%20Why%20don't%20you%20want%20the%20investigation%20to%20happen%3F%26quot%3B%20the%20bench%20asked%20Ms%20Singhania.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20counsel%20for%20Ms%20Singhania%20submitted%20to%20the%20court%20that%20no%20ingredients%20were%20made%20out%20in%20the%20complaint%20for%20registration%20of%20the%20FIR%20over%20the%20abetment%20of%20suicide.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20also%20submitted%20that%20Atul%20Subhash%20had%20not%20mentioned%20any%20act%20by%20his%20wife%20and%20family%20members%20which%20drew%20him%20to%20die%20by%20suicide.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20counsel%20further%20argued%20that%20the%20petitioner%20had%20the%20right%20to%20get%20legal%20remedies%20and%20couldn't%20be%20booked%20just%20for%20lodging%20a%20complaint%20against%20Atul%20Subhash.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20issued%20notices%20to%20respondents%20and%20directed%20them%20to%20file%20objections.%20The%20direction%20was%20also%20given%20for%20the%20prosecution%20to%20submit%20the%20materials%20collected%20during%20the%20investigation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20Bengaluru%20court%20on%20January%204%20granted%20bail%20to%20the%20estranged%20wife%20and%20in-laws%20of%20automobile%20firm%20executive%20Atul%20Subhash%2C%20who%20died%20by%20suicide%20in%20Bengaluru%20last%20month%20citing%20a%20troubled%20marriage%20and%20accusing%20his%20spouse%20of%20harassment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20family%20of%20Atul%20Subhash%20has%20stated%20that%20after%20obtaining%20the%20order%20sheet%2C%20they%20would%20appeal%20against%20the%20decision%20in%20the%20High%20Court%20of%20Karnataka.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bail%20was%20granted%20to%20Atul%20Subhash's%20wife%20Nikita%20Singhania%2C%20her%20mother%20Nisha%20Singhania%20and%20brother-in-law%20Anurag%20Singhania.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAtul%20Subhash%20died%20by%20suicide%20alleging%20his%20wife%20demanded%20Rs%203%20crore%20for%20divorce%20settlement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20police%20registered%20an%20FIR%20against%20the%20accused%20persons%20under%20Sections%20108%2C%203%20(5)%20of%20the%20Bharatiya%20Nyay%20Sanhita%20(BNS)%20on%20December%209.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBikas%20Kumar%20(Subhash's%20brother)%20had%20lodged%20a%20police%20complaint%20alleging%20abetment%20to%20suicide%20with%20the%20Marathahalli%20police%20in%20Bengaluru.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBikas%20Kumar%20alleged%20in%20the%20complaint%20that%20false%20cases%20were%20lodged%20against%20his%20brother%20(Atul%20Subhash)%20by%20the%20accused%2C%20demanding%20Rs%203%20crore%20to%20settle%20the%20case.%20He%20had%20also%20alleged%20that%20his%20brother%20was%20taunted%20in%20the%20court%20during%20the%20proceedings%20that%20he%20had%20to%20either%20give%20Rs%203%20crore%20or%20die%20by%20suicide.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Singhania's%20family%20had%20alleged%20that%20Subhash%20demanded%20a%20hefty%20dowry%20from%20her%20family%20which%20resulted%20in%20the%20death%20of%20her%20father.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPavan%20Kumar%20Modi%2C%20Atul%20Subhash's%20father%2C%20had%20stated%20that%20the%20family%20is%20worried%20about%20the%20safety%20of%20his%20grandson.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20the%20court%20grants%20bail%20to%20Atul's%20wife%2C%20she%20can%20attack%20the%20child%20and%20endanger%20his%20life.%20If%20she%20can%20drive%20my%20son%20to%20commit%20suicide%2C%20she%20can%20also%20do%20the%20same%20to%20the%20kid%20as%20well%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMy%20grandson%20was%20ATM%20to%20her.%20She%20got%20money%20on%20the%20pretext%20of%20taking%20care%20of%20him.%20She%20approached%20the%20High%20Court%20demanding%20Rs%2020%2C000%20to%20Rs%2040%2C000.%20She%20went%20on%20to%20appeal%20for%20Rs%2080%2C000.%20Even%20after%20this%2C%20she%20went%20on%20demanding%20more%20money.%20Hence%2C%20we%20have%20approached%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20for%20the%20custody%20of%20the%20child%20as%20he%20is%20safe%20with%20us%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20had%20stated.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1736173020000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg