hree%20cases%20of%20Human%20Metapneumovirus%20(HMPV)%20have%20been%20detected%20in%20India%20-%20two%20in%20Bengaluru%20and%20one%20in%20Ahmedabad.%20The%20cases%20were%20detected%20in%20babies%20and%20one%20of%20them%20has%20been%20discharged%20from%20the%20hospital.%20The%20Centre%2C%20as%20well%20as%20India's%20top%20medical%20body%2C%20the%20Indian%20Council%20for%20Medical%20Research%20(ICMR)%2C%20has%20said%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fhmpv-not-new-dont-panic-karnataka-as-2-cases-reported-in-bengaluru-7410920%5C%22%3EThere's%20no%20need%20to%20panic%3C%2Fa%3E%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3BHMPV%20is%20already%20in%20circulation%20globally%2C%20including%20in%20India.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20as%20reports%20of%20HMPV%20outbreak%20in%20China%20emerged%2C%20%23Lockdown%20started%20trending%20on%20social%20media%2C%20with%20people%20drawing%20parallels%20between%20the%20HMPV%20surge%20and%20the%20COVID-19%20outbreak%20in%202019-2020%20in%20China%2C%20which%20later%20led%20to%20a%20global%20pandemic.%20Covid%20cases%20were%20first%20reported%20in%20November%20in%20China's%20Wuhan%20and%20it%20rapidly%20spread%20to%20other%20countries.%20India%20reported%20its%20first%20case%20of%20COVID-19%20in%20January%202020%20in%20Kerala.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20was%20among%20the%20countries%20worst%20affected%20by%20the%20COVID-19%20outbreak%20after%20the%20US.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fexplainer-hmpv-not-new-pathogen-cases-have-been-reported-worldwide-7411648%5C%22%3EHMPV%20is%20a%20viral%20pathogen%20%3C%2Fa%3Ethat%20causes%20respiratory%20infections%20in%20people%20of%20all%20age%20groups.%20It%20was%20first%20discovered%20in%202001%20and%20is%20known%20to%20cause%20illnesses%20ranging%20from%20mild%20respiratory%20discomfort%20to%20severe%20complications%2C%20especially%20in%20vulnerable%20populations%20such%20as%20infants%2C%20older%20adults%20and%20individuals%20with%20weakened%20immune%20systems.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERead%20more%3A%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fno-hmpv-case-in-maharashtra-government-urges-citizens-to-follow-advisory-7412087%5C%22%3ENo%20HMPV%20Case%20In%20Maharashtra%2C%20Government%20Urges%20Citizens%20To%20Follow%20Advisory%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E'No%20Need%20To%20Panic'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPeople%20fear%20that%20the%20surge%20in%20HMPV%20cases%20could%20lead%20to%20another%20global%20outbreak%20and%20force%20governments%20to%20enforce%20a%20lockdown%20to%20control%20the%20spread.%20However%2C%20medical%20authorities%20are%20telling%20people%20%26quot%3Bnot%20to%20panic%26quot%3B%20since%20the%20virus%20has%20been%20under%20circulation%20globally%20and%20is%20not%20a%20new%20pathogen.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20emphasized%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fhmpv-already-in-circulation-including-in-india-top-medical-body-icmr-7410226%5C%22%3EHMPV%20is%20already%20in%20circulation%20globally%2C%20including%20in%20India%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20cases%20of%20respiratory%20illnesses%20associated%20with%20HMPV%20have%20been%20reported%20in%20various%20countries.%20Furthermore%2C%20based%20on%20current%20data%20from%20ICMR%20and%20the%20Integrated%20Disease%20Surveillance%20Programme%20(IDSP)%20network%2C%20there%20has%20been%20no%20unusual%20surge%20in%20Influenza-Like%20Illness%20(ILI)%20or%20Severe%20Acute%20Respiratory%20Illness%20(SARI)%20cases%20in%20the%20country%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20ICMR%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20don't%20think%20we%20should%20be%20pressing%20the%20panic%20button%2C%20because%20HMPV%20is%20not%20a%20new%20virus%2C%20it%20already%20exists.%20Reports%20suggest%20that%20it%20is%20the%20first%20case%20of%20HMPV%20in%20India%2C%20this%20is%20not%20true%20because%20HMPV%20is%20an%20existing%20virus%2C%20and%20a%20certain%20percentage%20of%20people%20do%20get%20affected%20by%20this%20virus%20and%20it%20is%20not%20something%20new%2C%26quot%3B%20Karnataka's%20Health%20Minister%20Dinesh%20Gundu%20Rao%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDirectorate%20General%20of%20Health%20Services%20(DGHS)%20official%2C%20Dr%20Atul%20Goel%2C%20assured%20people%20that%2C%20%26quot%3BThere%20has%20been%20news%20doing%20the%20rounds%20about%20a%20Metapneumovirus%20outbreak%20in%20China.%20Let%20me%20be%20very%20clear%20on%20that%20count.%20Metapneumovirus%20is%20like%20any%20other%20respiratory%20virus%20which%20causes%20the%20common%20cold%2C%20and%20in%20the%20very%20old%20and%20the%20very%20young%20it%20could%20cause%20flu-like%20symptoms.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHuman%20Metapneumovirus%20(HMPV)%20is%20not%20a%20new%20virus.%20It%20has%20been%20part%20of%20the%20circulating%20flu%20virus%20in%20India%20for%20long.%20Hence%2C%20the%20majority%20of%20the%20Indian%20population%20has%20developed%20immunity%20against%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20Dr%20Harshal%20R%20Salve%2C%20Additional%20Professor%2C%20Centre%20for%20Community%20Medicine%20at%20AIIMS%2C%20New%20Delhi%2C%20told%20IANS.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20added%20that%20the%20%26quot%3Bchances%20of%20severe%20disease%20are%20very%20rare.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20To%20Protect%20Yourself%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDos%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ECover%20mouth%20and%20nose%20with%20a%20handkerchief%20or%20tissue%20paper%20when%20coughing%20or%20sneezing%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EWash%20hands%20frequently%20with%20soap%2C%20water%2C%20or%20alcohol-based%20sanitiser%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EStay%20away%20from%20public%20places%20if%20anyone%20has%20a%20fever%2C%20cough%2C%20or%20sneeze%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EDrink%20plenty%20of%20water%20and%20eat%20a%20nutritious%20diet%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EMaintain%20adequate%20ventilation%20in%20all%20areas%20to%20reduce%20infection.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDon'ts%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAvoid%20Handshake%2C%20tissue%20paper%20and%20handkerchief%20recycling%2C%20close%20contact%20with%20sick%20people%2C%20frequent%20touching%20of%20eyes%2C%20nose%20and%20mouth%2C%20spitting%20in%20public%20places%2C%20and%20medicines%20without%20doctor's%20advice.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECurrently%2C%20there%20is%20no%20specific%20antiviral%20medication%20or%20vaccine%20available%20for%20HMPV.%20Treatment%20is%20supportive%20and%20depends%20on%20the%20severity%20of%20the%20infection.%20For%20mild%20cases%2C%20rest%2C%20adequate%20hydration%20and%20over-the-counter%20medications%20to%20manage%20fever%20and%20nasal%20congestion%20are%20sufficient.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1736167440000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-01%2Ffi1f12gg_hmpv_625x300_06_January_25.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fhmpv-cases-amid-hmpv-worry-lockdown-trends-government-says-no-need-to-panic-7412563%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Three%20cases%20of%20Human%20Metapneumovirus%20(HMPV)%20have%20been%20detected%20in%20India%20-%20two%20in%20Bengaluru%20and%20one%20in%20Ahmedabad.%20The%20cases%20were%20detected%20in%20babies%20and%20one%20of%20them%20has%20been%20discharged%20from%20the%20hospital.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fhmpv-cases-amid-hmpv-worry-lockdown-trends-government-says-no-need-to-panic-7412563%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22HMPV%20Not%20New%20Virus%2C%20Majority%20Indian%20Population%20Immune%20To%20It%3A%20Experts%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Human%20Metapneumovirus%20(HMPV)%20is%20not%20a%20new%20virus%20and%20most%20of%20the%20Indian%20population%20is%20immune%20to%20it%2C%20said%20health%20experts%20on%20Monday%2C%20even%20as%20the%20number%20of%20reported%20cases%20climbed%20to%20three%20in%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Monday%2C%20health%20officials%20in%20the%20country%20reported%20three%20cases%20of%20HMPV%20--%20babies%20aged%20three-%20and%20eight-month-old%20from%20Bengaluru%20(Karnataka)%20and%20a%20two-year-old%20child%20in%20Gujarat's%20Ahmedabad.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHuman%20Metapneumovirus%20(HMPV)%20is%20not%20a%20new%20virus.%20It%20has%20been%20part%20of%20the%20circulating%20flu%20virus%20in%20India%20for%20long.%20Hence%2C%20the%20majority%20of%20the%20Indian%20population%20has%20developed%20immunity%20against%20it%2C%E2%80%9D%20Dr.%20Harshal%20R%20Salve%2C%20Additional%20Professor%2C%20Centre%20for%20Community%20Medicine%20at%20AIIMS%2C%20New%20Delhi%2C%20told%20IANS.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20added%20that%20the%20%E2%80%9Cchances%20of%20a%20severe%20disease%20are%20very%20rare%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHMPV%20was%20first%20discovered%20in%202001%20and%20is%20part%20of%20the%20Pneumoviridae%20family%20along%20with%20the%20Respiratory%20syncytial%20virus%20(RSV).%20The%20symptoms%20commonly%20associated%20with%20HMPV%20include%20cough%2C%20fever%2C%20nasal%20congestion%2C%20and%20shortness%20of%20breath.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CLike%20for%20any%20other%20flu%20viruses%2C%20elderly%20people%2C%20children%20and%20people%20with%20comorbidities%20must%20take%20care.%20There%20is%20no%20need%20to%20create%20panic%2C%20and%20one%20should%20stop%20rumour-mongering%20in%20the%20public%2C%E2%80%9D%20Salve%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20two%20cases%20from%20Karnataka%20were%20detected%20via%20routine%20surveillance%20by%20ICMR%20in%20a%203-month-old%20girl%20and%20an%208-month-old%20boy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBoth%20had%20a%20history%20of%20bronchopneumonia%20--%20a%20form%20of%20pneumonia%2C%20a%20lung%20infection%2C%20and%20were%20admitted%20to%20a%20private%20hospital.%20Bronchopneumonia%20affects%20both%20the%20alveoli%20in%20the%20lungs%20and%20the%20bronchi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Health%20Ministry%20informed%20that%20while%20the%20baby%20girl%20%E2%80%9Chas%20been%20discharged%E2%80%9D%2C%20the%20baby%20boy%20%E2%80%9Cis%20now%20recovering%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20third%20case%2C%20the%20child%2C%20from%20Rajasthan%2C%20was%20admitted%20to%20a%20private%20hospital%20in%20Chandkheda's%20area%20of%20Ahmedabad%2C%20after%20showing%20symptoms%20of%20cold%20and%20cough.%20The%20child%20is%20stable%20now%2C%20reports%20quoted%20civic%20officials%20as%20saying.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHMPV%20is%20not%20a%20new%20virus.%20It%20commonly%20causes%20colds%20among%20children%20and%20also%20some%20adults.%20For%20self-limiting%20colds%2C%20we%20don't%20do%20expensive%20tests%20to%20diagnose%20which%20specific%20virus%20it%20is%20due%20to.%20Therefore%2C%20the%20finding%20of%20this%20virus%20upon%20testing%20is%20not%20anything%20unusual%20or%20worrisome%2C%E2%80%9D%20Dr%20Rajeev%20Jayadevan%2C%20Chairman%20of%20the%20Kerala%20State%20IMA%20Research%20Cell%2C%20told%20IANS.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAll%20over%20the%20world%2C%20HMPV%20is%20a%20well-known%20cause%20of%20common%20cold%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHMPV%20is%20already%20in%20circulation%20globally%2C%20including%20in%20India%2C%20and%20cases%20of%20respiratory%20illnesses%20associated%20with%20HMPV%20have%20been%20reported%20in%20various%20countries%2C%20particularly%20in%20China.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CCommon%20cold%20is%20more%20common%20in%20winter%2C%20therefore%20it%20is%20being%20reported%20from%20China%20at%20this%20time.%20People%20should%20not%20get%20the%20impression%20that%20a%20new%20virus%20from%20China%20has%20now%20reached%20Bangalore%2C%E2%80%9D%20Jayadevan%20told%20IANS.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENotably%2C%20the%20three%20cases%20of%20HMPV%20have%20no%20travel%20history.%20Thus%2C%20it%20currently%20remains%20unknown%20whether%20the%20cases%20are%20related%20to%20the%20outbreak%20seen%20in%20China.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThey%20(infected%20children)%20have%20not%20traveled%20to%20China%2C%20Malaysia%2C%20or%20any%20other%20country.%20The%20outbreak%20in%20China%20is%20linked%20to%20a%20new%20variant%20of%20HMPV.%20We%20do%20not%20yet%20have%20full%20details%2C%20and%20the%20government%20is%20still%20gathering%20information%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Karnataka%20Health%20Minister%20Dinesh%20Gundu%20Rao%2C%20while%20speaking%20to%20the%20media.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHMPV%20isn't%20new.%20What%20we%20don't%20know%20is%20whether%20the%20strain%20is%20novel%20and%20has%20a%20virulence%20that's%20different%20from%20what%20we've%20experienced%20in%20the%20past.%20Unless%20one%20knows%20that%20it%20is%20a%20novel%20strain%2C%20cases%20have%20been%20detected%20all%20the%20time!%20Hopefully%2C%20whole%20genome%20sequencing%20and%20clinical%20information%20will%20clarify%20soon%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Lancelot%20Pinto%2C%20an%20Indian%20pulmonologist%20and%20epidemiologist%2C%20in%20a%20post%20on%20social%20media%20platform%20X.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20the%20government%20has%20issued%20precautionary%20measures%20such%20as%20covering%20mouth%20and%20nose%20with%20handkerchiefs%20or%20tissue%20paper%20while%20coughing%2C%20or%20sneezing%3B%20washing%20hands%20often%20with%20soap%20and%20water%20or%20alcohol-based%20sanitizer%3B%20avoiding%20crowded%20places%3B%20staying%20away%20from%20public%20places%20while%20having%20fever%2C%20cough%2C%20or%20sneezing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1736166000000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-07%2Fpnobi8q_hospital-generic-_625x300_20_July_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fhmpv-not-new-virus-majority-indian-population-immune-to-it-experts-7411484%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Human%20Metapneumovirus%20(HMPV)%20is%20not%20a%20new%20virus%20and%20most%20of%20the%20Indian%20population%20is%20immune%2