who%20is%20recovering%20in%20the%20hospital%20and%20a%20three-month-old%20who%20has%20been%20discharged%20were%20the%20first%20reported%20cases%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2F3-month-old-and-8-month-old-babies-diagnosed-with-hmpv-in-bengaluru-7409670%5C%22%3EHMPV%20in%20India.%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0Later%2C%20a%20two-month-old%20also%20tested%20positive%20in%20Ahmedabad.%20Currently%2C%20China%20is%20witnessing%20an%20HMPV%20outbreak.%20According%20to%20social%20media%20posts%2C%20multiple%20viruses%2C%20including%20influenza%20A%2C%20HMPV%2C%20Mycoplasma%20pneumoniae%2C%20and%20COVID-19%2C%20are%20circulating%20in%20China.%20Several%20videos%20and%20posts%20on%20social%20media%20suggest%20that%20hospitals%20are%20overwhelmed%20with%20individuals%20struggling%20with%20respiratory%20illnesses.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHMPV%2C%20first%20identified%20in%202001%2C%20is%20a%20respiratory%20infection%20that%20causes%20flu-like%20symptoms.%20It%20can%20affect%20people%20of%20all%20ages%2C%20however%2C%20young%20children(below%205%20years)%2C%20older%20adults%20and%20those%20with%20weakened%20immune%20systems%20are%20at%20a%20higher%20risk.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3ESymptoms%20of%20HMPV%3A%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECough%2C%20fever%2C%20nasal%20congestion%2C%20shortness%20of%20breath%2C%20and%20sore%20throat%20are%20a%20few%20symptoms%20of%20HMPV.%20These%20symptoms%20usually%20show%20up%20three%20to%20six%20days%20after%20you%20have%20been%20exposed%20to%20the%20virus.%20Severe%20illness%20due%20to%20HMPV%20may%20require%20hospitalisation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3EHow%20is%20HMPV%20transmitted%3F%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fhealth%2Fnew-virus-outbreak-in-china-what-is-hmpv-know-symptoms-prevention-tips-and-more-7389823%5C%22%3EHMPV%3C%2Fa%3E%20spreads%20through%20direct%20contact%20with%20someone%20who%20has%20it.%20Touching%20contaminated%20surfaces%2C%20coughing%2C%20sneezing%20and%20shaking%20hands%20can%20spread%20the%20virus.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20symptoms%20worsen%2C%20one%20may%20develop%20severe%20cough%2C%20wheezing%20and%20shortness%20of%20breath.%20In%20such%20cases%2C%20it%20is%20crucial%20to%20seek%20medical%20assistance%20immediately.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3ETreatment%20and%20vaccination%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECurrently%2C%20there%20is%20no%20vaccine%20against%20HMPV.%20Treatment%20is%20mostly%20geared%20toward%20easing%20symptoms.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3EHow%20to%20differentiate%20between%20common%20cold%20and%20HMPV%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHMPV%20usually%20causes%20symptoms%20similar%20to%20the%20common%20cold%2C%20but%20some%20individuals%20can%20get%20very%20sick.%20Those%20infected%20for%20the%20first%20time%20with%20HMPV%20are%20more%20likely%20to%20get%20severely%20sick.%20Symptoms%20are%20milder%20if%20you%20get%20another%20HMPV%20infection.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3ETips%20to%20prevent%20HMPV%3A%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYou%20can%20reduce%20the%20risk%20of%20getting%20HMPV%20and%20other%20respiratory%20illnesses%20with%20these%20steps%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EWash%20hands%20with%20soap%20and%20water%20for%20atleast%2020%20seconds%20or%20use%20an%20alcohol-based%20hand%20sanitiser%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ECover%20your%20mouth%20and%20nose%20while%20coughing%20or%20sneezing%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EConsider%20wearing%20a%20mask%20and%20avoid%20contact%20with%20those%20who%20are%20sick%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EAvoid%20touching%20your%20eyes%2C%20nose%20and%20mouth%20with%20unwashed%20hands%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EPractice%20self-isolation%20if%20you%20are%20sick%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndividuals%20with%20preexisting%20lung%20diseases%20should%20be%20extra%20cautious%20and%20must%20follow%20all%20precautions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EDisclaimer%3A%20This%20content%20including%20advice%20provides%20generic%20information%20only.%20It%20is%20in%20no%20way%20a%20substitute%20for%20a%20qualified%20medical%20opinion.%20Always%20consult%20a%20specialist%20or%20your%20own%20doctor%20for%20more%20information.%20NDTV%20does%20not%20claim%20responsibility%20for%20this%20information.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1736163300000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-01%2Fpoqoq0rg_virus-spread_625x300_03_January_25.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fhealth%2Fhealth-ministry-confirms-three-hmpv-cases-in-india-know-symptoms-and-prevention-steps-7410083%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22HMPV%20symptoms%20are%20similar%20to%20those%20of%20flu%20or%20common%20cold.%20It%20can%20spread%20from%20an%20infected%20individual%20to%20others%20through%20coughing%2C%20sneezing%20or%20personal%20contact.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fhealth%2Fhealth-ministry-confirms-three-hmpv-cases-in-india-know-symptoms-and-prevention-steps-7410083%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%229%20Killed%20After%20Maoists%20Blow%20Up%20Security%20Vehicle%20In%20Chhattisgarh%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EEight%20jawans%20and%20a%20driver%20were%20killed%20in%20Chhattisgarh's%20Bijapur%20district%20when%20Maoists%20used%20an%20Improvised%20Explosive%20Device%20(IED)%20to%20blow%20up%20their%20vehicle.%20The%20nine%20were%20returning%20from%20an%20operation%20when%20the%20IED%20blew%20up%20the%20Scorpio%20SUV%20at%20Kutru%20in%20the%20Bastar%20region%20around%202.15%20pm.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20today%2C%20security%20forces%20attacked%20Maoists%20in%20the%20Abujhmad%20region%20of%20Chhattisgarh%20and%20killed%20five%20rebels%2C%20including%20two%20women.%20Automatic%20weapons%20such%20as%20AK%2047%20and%20Self-Loading%20Rifles%20have%20been%20recovered.%20It%20was%20this%20operation%20that%20the%20jawans%20were%20returning%20from%20when%20the%20rebels%20targeted%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20eight%20security%20personnel%20belonged%20to%20the%20District%20Reserve%20Guard%2C%20a%20specialised%20police%20unit%20set%20up%20to%20tackle%20Maoism%20in%20the%20state.%20Visuals%20showed%20a%20massive%20crater%20at%20the%20spot%2C%20suggesting%20the%20intensity%20of%20the%20IED%20blast%20that%20killed%20the%20jawans.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Maoist%20attack%20comes%20against%20the%20backdrop%20of%20security%20forces%20making%20deep%20inroads%20into%20the%20Maoist-dominated%20areas%20of%20Chhattisgarh%20and%20cornering%20the%20rebels.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChhattisgarh%20Chief%20Minister%20Vishnudev%20Sai%20condemned%20the%20blast%20and%20described%20it%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bheinous%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Btragic%26quot%3B%20incident.%20%26quot%3BThis%20incident%20is%20extremely%20unfortunate.%20I%20pay%20tribute%20to%20the%20brave%20soldiers%20who%20sacrificed%20their%20lives%20and%20express%20my%20heartfelt%20condolences%20to%20their%20families.%20A%20thorough%20investigation%20and%20assessment%20of%20this%20attack%20are%20underway.%20I%20assure%20you%20that%20the%20sacrifices%20of%20our%20soldiers%20will%20not%20go%20in%20vain.%20The%20government%20is%20fully%20committed%20to%20eradicating%20Naxalism%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Chief%20Minister%20added%20that%20Union%20Home%20Minister%20Amit%20Shah%20has%20resolved%20to%20eliminate%20Maoism%20from%20the%20country%20by%20March%202026.%20%26quot%3BI%20am%20confident%20that%20by%20then%2C%20even%20the%20five%20Naxal-affected%20districts%20of%20Bastar%20will%20be%20free%20from%20Naxalism%2C%20and%20peace%20will%20be%20restored%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Chief%20Minister%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInspector%20General%20of%20Police%2C%20Bastar%2C%20Sundarraj%20Pattilingam%20said%20the%20IED%20blast%20targeted%20the%20jawans%20when%20they%20were%20returning%20to%20the%20camp%20after%20the%20operation.%20%26quot%3BFor%20the%20past%20two-three%20days%2C%20we%20were%20carrying%20out%20operations%20in%20the%20area.%20Five%20Maoists%20and%20a%20security%20personnel%20were%20killed%20in%20this%20operation.%20Security%20personnel%20were%20returning%20to%20the%20base%20camp%20after%20the%20operation%20when%20one%20vehicle%20was%20blown%20up%20in%20an%20IED%20blast.%20We%20will%20share%20detailed%20information%20after%20examining%20the%20blast%20site%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20senior%20officer%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20sources%2C%20the%20explosion%20was%20so%20powerful%20that%20a%20part%20of%20the%20Scorpio's%20bonnet%20was%20left%20hanging%20on%20a%20nearby%20tree.%20The%20blast%20site%20suggests%20that%20the%20Maoists%20used%20a%20foxhole%20technique%20for%20the%20explosion%2C%20the%20sources%20said.%20In%20this%20technique%2C%20Maoists%20dig%20holes%20and%20fill%20them%20up%20with%20stones.%20These%20holes%20are%20not%20detected%20during%20anti-mine%20operations.%20When%20Maoists%20intend%20to%20execute%20a%20blast%2C%20they%20place%20explosives%20in%20these%20holes%20and%20trigger%20an%20explosion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESources%20also%20said%20DRG%20personnel%20usually%20travel%20on%20foot%20or%20bikes%2C%20raising%20concerns%20about%20whether%20there%20was%20a%20violation%20of%20the%20Standard%20Operating%20Procedure%20in%20this%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1736163000000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-01%2Fus8jk70o_maoist-attack_625x300_06_January_25.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2F2-jawans-killed-after-maoists-blow-up-security-vehicle-in-chhattisgarh-7411144%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%222%20Jawans%20Killed%20After%20Maoists%20Blow%20Up%20Security%20Vehicle%20In%20Chhattisgarh%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2F2-jawans-killed-after-maoists-blow-up-security-vehicle-in-chhattisgarh-7411144%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Opinion%3A%20Is%20'Soft%20Hindutva'%20Helping%20AAP%3F%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-02%2Fh8avgdgg_arvind-kejriwal-_625x300_12_February_24.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20battle%20for%20Delhi%20is%20heating%20up%2C%20with%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%20and%20the%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party%20(AAP)%20engaged%20in%20a%20daily%20poster%20war.%20While%20the%20BJP%20and%20the%20Congress%20are%20in%20the%20process%20of%20finalising%20candidates%20for%20all%20seats%2C%20the%20AAP%2C%20in%20its%20final%20candidate%20list%2C%20denied%20tickets%20to%2020%20MLAs.%20While%20the%20BJP%20is%20hoping%20to%20make%20a%20comeback%20in%20Delhi%20after%20three%20decades%2C%20the%20AAP%20aims%20to%20score%20a%20hattrick%2C%20with%20the%20Congress%2C%20too%2C%20vying%20to%20open%20its%20account.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20AAP%2C%20facing%20the%20biggest%20battle%20since%20its%20inception%2C%20is%20battling%2010%20years%20of%20natural%20anti-incumbency%20as%20its%20leaders%20face%20serious%20corruption%20allegations.%20It%20has%20announced%20a%20series%20of%20freebies%20that%20will%20be%20implemented%20if%20voters%20back%20the%20party.%20It%20has%20also%20employed%20a%20%E2%80%98soft%20Hindutva'%20strategy%20to%20challenge%20the%20BJP%20head-on.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ENo%20Less%20Hindu%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20AAP%20is%20out%20to%20prove%20that%20it%20is%20no%20less%20a%20Hindu%20party%20than%20the%20BJP.%20In%20that%20spirit%2C%20it%20has%20announced%20the%20Pujari%20Granthi%20Samman%20Yojana%20to%20give%20an%20honorarium%20to%20the%20priests%20of%20temples%20and%20the%20'granthis'%20of%20the%20Gurudwara%20of%20%E2%82%B918%2C000%20per%20month.%20The%20AAP%20claims%20this%20is%20the%20first%20scheme%20of%20its%20kind%20in%20the%20country%2C%20accusing%20the%20BJP%20of%20not%20honouring%20priests%20in%20the%20states%20ruled%20by%20them%20or%20their%20allies.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDelhi%20Chief%20Minister%20Atishi%20fired%20another%20salvo%20at%20the%20BJP%2C%20accusing%20the%20Lieutenant-Governor%20(L-G)%20of%20approving%20the%20demolition%20of%20temples%20in%20the%20national%20capital.%20Speaking%20on%20the%20matter%2C%20Atishi%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20BJP%20central%20government%20is%20planning%20to%20demolish%20temples%20and%20Buddhist%20temples%20in%20different%20parts%20of%20Delhi.%20The%20dual%20face%20of%20the%20BJP%20is%20exposed%E2%80%94they%20claim%20to%20protect%20Hinduism%2C%20yet%20they%20secretly%20order%20the%20destruction%20of%20these%20sacred%20places.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20essence%2C%20the%20AAP%20is%20hoping%20to%20put%20the%20BJP%20on%20the%20back%20foot.%20It%20does%20not%20want%20to%20go%20the%20Congress%20way%2C%20which%20has%20been%20branded%20as%20%E2%80%98anti-Hindu'%20or%20%E2%80%98pro-Muslim'%20by%20the%20BJP%20and%20its%20supporters.%20It%20does%20not%20want%20to%20be%20seen%20as%20doing%20%E2%80%98minority%20appeasement'%20politics.%20It%20is%20cognisant%20of%20the%20fact%20that%20its%20performance%20in%20Kejriwal's%20second%20full%20term%20(2020-25)%20has%20been%20weaker%20compared%20to%20its%20first%20full%20term%20(2015-20)%2C%20and%20wishes%20to%20deflect%20the%20issue.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20turn%2C%20the%20BJP%20is%20now%20under%20pressure%20too%20to%20announce%20a%20similar%20scheme%20for%20Hindu%20priests%20in%20its%20manifesto.%20It%20has%20also%20alleged%20that%20the%20AAP%20is%20making%20false%20claims%20about%20the%20razing%20of%20temples.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EZero-Risk%20Strategy%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress's%20own%20similar%20strategy%20in%20the%20past%20had%20yielded%20limited%20success.%20However%2C%20for%20the%20AAP%2C%20strategists%20feel%20this%20is%20a%20zero-risk%20approach%20as%20the%20party%20already%20has%20the%20majority%20support%20of%20minorities%2C%20and%20thus%2C%20the%20leakage%20to%20the%20Congress%20could%20be%20minimal.%20The%20AAP%20is%20better%20placed%20to%20defeat%20the%20BJP%E2%80%94it%20received%2083%25%20Muslim%20and%2067%25%20Sikh%20community%20support%20in%20the%202020%20assembly%20polls%E2%80%94and%20this%20could%20help%20the%20party%20consolidate%20the%20minority%20vote.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKejriwal%20has%20admitted%20that%20the%20AAP%20has%20not%20been%20able%20to%20fulfil%20several%20promises%E2%80%94mainly%2C%20reduction%20of%20air%20pollution%2C%20construction%20of%20roads%20and%20the%20cleaning%20of%20Yamuna.%20Apart%20from%20free%20bus%20travel%20for%20women%2C%20no%20significant%20new%20scheme%20has%20been%20implemented.%20The%20party%20was%20busy%20fighting%20a%20political-legal%20battle%20as%20several%20of%20its%20ministers%2C%20including%20Kejriwal%2C%20were%20put%20behind%20bars.%20The%20administration%20in%20Delhi%20was%20hit%20severely.%20Even%20Kejriwal%20admitted%20that%20his%20party%20has%20not%20been%20able%20to%20implement%20some%20schemes%2C%20including%20the%20Mahila%20Samman%20Yojana.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat's%20not%20all.%20The%20victory%20in%20the%20Municipal%20Corporation%20of%20Delhi%20(MCD)%20polls%20in%202022%20has%20added%20another%20layer%20of%20anti-incumbency%3A%20it%20can%20no%20longer%20blame%20the%20BJP%20for%20the%20city's%20civic%20issues%2C%20such%20as%20sewage%20problems%20and%20lack%20of%20cleanliness.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20AAP%20realises%20that%20it's%20at%20risk%20of%20losing%20support%20among%20%3Cem%3Elabharthis%20%3C%2Fem%3Eand%20Delhiites%20at%20large.%20Which%20is%20why%20it%20is%20trying%20to%20deflect%20attention%20towards%20Hindutva.%20The%20BJP%2C%20meanwhile%2C%20has%20countered%20by%20saying%20that%20it%20is%20the%20original%20Hindutva%20party.%20In%20doing%20so%2C%20it%20runs%20the%20risk%20of%20losing%20focus%20on%20the%20anti-incumbency%20against%20the%20AAP%20government%20and%20its%20MLAs%2C%20which%20it%20can%20exploit.%20Since%20the%20BJP%20doesn't%20have%20a%20chief%20ministerial%20face%2C%20it%20can%20win%20only%20by%20adopting%20a%20hyper-local%2C%20seat-by-seat%20approach.%20The%20AAP%20is%20driving%20the%20agenda%20and%20the%20BJP%20is%20seen%20as%20merely%20reacting%20to%20it.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEven%20so%2C%20the%20AAP%20needs%20to%20be%20cautious.%20Dabbling%20with%20Hindutva%20is%20like%20playing%20on%20the%20BJP's%20own%20pitch.%20It%20can%20backfire%2C%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Amitabh%20Tiwari%20is%20a%20political%20strategist%20and%20commentator.%20In%20his%20earlier%20avatar%2C%20he%20was%20a%20corporate%20and%20investment%20banker.)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1736159520000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-02%2Fh8avgdgg_arvind-kejriwal-_625x300_12_February_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fis-soft-hindutva-helping-aap-7411540%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20AAP%20realises%20that%20it%20is%20at%20risk%20of%20losing%20support%20among%20labharthis%20and%20Delhiites%20at%20large.%20Which%20is%20why%20it%20is%20trying%20to%20deflect%20attention%20towards%20Hindutva.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fis-soft-hindutva-helping-aap-7411540%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Djokovic%20still%20has%20'trauma'%20over%20Covid%20deportation%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1736158160000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Face%2Fbranded_sport%2F1200%2Fcpsprodpb%2F7e93%2Flive%2F4b151a10-cc0d-11ef-95ee-b7d7e6412a71.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fsport%2Ftennis%2Farticles%2Fc3e3lg8w015o%231%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Novak%20Djokovic%20says%20he%20still%20has%20%26quot%3Btrauma%26quot%3B%20when%20he%20visits%20Melbourne%2C%20three%20years%20after%20being%20deported%20becau