%20Farming%20Business%20Makes%20Rs%202%20Lakh%2FMonth%20%26amp%3B%20Trains%2010%2C000%20Farmers%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20faced%20many%20challenges%2C%20but%20I%20never%20let%20them%20deter%20me.%20No%20matter%20how%20tough%20things%20got%2C%20I%20knew%20I%20could%20make%20it%20work.%20I%20just%20had%20to%20keep%20going%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Pratibha%20Jha%2C%2040%2C%20whose%20journey%20holds%20true%20the%20statement%20that%20with%20focused%20effort%2C%20anything%20is%20within%20reach.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGrowing%20up%20in%20Muzaffarpur%2C%20Bihar%2C%20a%2010-year-old%20Pratibha%20would%20often%20watch%20local%20farmers%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F380434%2Ftrupti-dhakate-mushroom-farming-sustainable-eco-friendly-women-entrepreneur%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecultivate%20mushrooms%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%E2%80%9CI%20was%20always%20curious%20about%20how%20mushrooms%20grew%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%20%E2%80%9CSomething%20about%20it%20fascinated%20me%2C%20but%20I%20never%20thought%20it%20could%20be%20my%20livelihood%20one%20day.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHer%20life%20took%20a%20sudden%20turn%20when%20her%20father%20passed%20away%2C%20and%20at%20the%20young%20age%20of%2015%2C%20she%20was%20married%20off%20to%20an%20engineer%20from%20Bihar%E2%80%99s%20Darbhanga.%20After%20moving%20to%20her%20husband%E2%80%99s%20place%20in%20Mirzapur%20Hansi%20village%2C%20her%20interest%20in%20mushroom%20farming%20lingered%2C%20but%20the%20practicalities%20of%20starting%20a%20business%20seemed%20out%20of%20reach.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%222400846096%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhen%20I%20spoke%20to%20people%20in%20my%20v