outside%20my%20house%20%E2%80%94%20not%20because%20I%20didn%E2%80%99t%20like%20them%2C%20but%20because%20I%20was%20scared%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20laughs.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20500px)%20100vw%2C%20500px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FIMG-20241208-WA0127-1733988839-500x889.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20Pawsitivity%20worker%20gently%20pets%20a%20dog%20proudly%20wearing%20one%20of%20the%20reflective%20collars%20she%20helped%20create.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FIMG-20241208-WA0127-1733988839-500x889.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FIMG-20241208-WA0127-1733988839-169x300.jpg%20169w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FIMG-20241208-WA0127-1733988839-150x267.jpg%20150w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FIMG-20241208-WA0127-1733988839.jpg%20631w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-388999%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22889%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EPawsitivity%E2%80%99s%20reflective%20collars%20help%20prevent%20accidents%20by%20making%20strays%20visible%20to%20drivers%20at%20night%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERimjhim%2C%20who%20was%20more%20than%20pleased%20to%20help%20somebody%20so%20close%20to%20her%2C%20then%20decided%20that%20since%20their%20very%20first%20employee%20was%20a%20woman%20who%20could%20use%20a%20little%20push%2C%20they%20would%20exclusively%20work%20with%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F380268%2Findiegood-sneha-baghrecha-sustainable-eco-friendly-pet-products-india-collaborations-animal-welfare-artisan-crafts-yoda-pfa%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eunderprivileged%20w