d%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20jam%2C%20ropes%2C%20mats%2C%20and%20coasters.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20month%2C%20the%20organisation%20converts%20about%20300%20tonnes%20of%20banana%20waste%20into%20useful%20products.%20Through%20offline%20and%20online%20markets%20and%20exhibitions%2C%20Kasinath%20has%20established%20a%20market%20for%20the%20products%20in%20various%20districts%20of%20Odisha%2C%20West%20Bengal%2C%20Chhattisgarh%2C%20and%20Andhra%20Pradesh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnusuya%20travels%2025%20km%20from%20her%20home%20in%20Bhubaneswar%20to%20the%20facility%20every%20morning%20to%20oversee%20daily%20operations.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20a%20CCTV%20camera%2C%20but%20the%20team%20still%20needs%20guidance%20and%20monitoring.%20I%20also%20meet%20delegates%20and%20visitors%20at%20the%20centre.%20I%20don%E2%80%99t%20earn%20an%20income%20from%20this%3B%20our%20goal%20is%20simply%20to%20help%20our%20farmer%20brothers%20earn%20extra%20income%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Anusuya%2C%20the%20president%20of%20the%20association.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20adds%2C%20%E2%80%9CMy%20husband%20and%20I%20have%20been%20working%20in%20the%20social%20development%20sector%20for%20over%20two%20decades%2C%20focusing%20on%20human%20rights.%20We%20were%20inspired%20to%20take%20up%20initiatives%20that%20boost%20the%20income%20of%20rural%20residents.%E2%80%9D%20Besides%20her%20role%20in%20the%20association%2C%20Anusuya%20also%20works%20as%20a%20translator.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20innovative%20approach%20not%20only%20addresses%20the%20waste%20problem%20but%20also%20generates%20additional%20income%20for%20farmers.%20Currently%2C%20at%20least%201%2C000%20farmers%20across%20Kordha%2C%20Cuttack%2C%20and%20Puri%20districts%20of%20Odisha%20are%20reaping%20the%20benefits%20of%20the%20association.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20approach%20provides%20a%20valuable%20template%20for%20rural%20development%20and%20demonstrates%20the%20potential%20of%20waste-to-wealth%20initiatives%20in%20promoting%20sustainable%20agricultural%20practices%20and%20improving%20the%20livelihoods%20of%20rural%20communities%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Kasinath.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CFor%20every%20stem%2C%20we%20give%20Rs%2070-80%20to%20a%20farmer.%20By%20collecting%20waste%20from%20farm%20sites%2C%20we%20clean%20their%20field.%20This%20indirectly%20helps%20them%20as%20it%20saves%20them%20labour%20costs.%20On%20average%2C%20a%20farmer%20associated%20with%20us%20earns%20an%20additional%20Rs%207%2C000%20to%20Rs%2010%2C000%20for%20banana%20waste%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20initiative%E2%80%99s%20impact%20extends%20beyond%20the%20economic%20realm.%20%E2%80%9CBy%20removing%20banana%20waste%20from%20the%20fields%2C%20this%20approach%20contributes%20to%20a%20cleaner%20environment.%20The%20elimination%20of%20open%20burning%20prevents%20air%20pollution%20and%20mitigates%20the%20risk%20of%20soil%20contamination%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20Kasinath%2C%20this%20work%20is%20purely%20selfless.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20is%20an%20association%20of%20farmers.%20Around%2040%20people%20are%20employed%20here%20to%20handle%20the%20processing%20work%2C%20and%20they%20earn%20a%20salary%20from%20the%20profits.%20I%20don%E2%80%99t%20take%20any%20share%20of%20the%20earnings%20%E2%80%94%20I%20sustain%20myself%20through%20my%20consultancy%20work%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says%2C%20adding%2C%20%E2%80%9CThis%20is%20my%20way%20of%20contributing%20to%20the%20betterment%20of%20society%20and%20supporting%20my%20farmer%20brothers.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat%3B%20All%20photos%20courtesy%20Kasinath%20Jena%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1735620427000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2Fbanana-waste-4-1734954508.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D391779%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20Odisha%E2%80%99s%20Khordha%20district%2C%2